HEADWORD: Unfeudalize
<hw>Un*feu"dal*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>feudalize</ets>.]</ety> <def>To free from feudal
customs or character; to make not feudal.</def>
<rj><au>Carlyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
